  "detailed_description": "Song of a Spirit is a Game Jam submission made in 14 days. It is a crafting game that explores an unconstrained approach to writing tunes, rhythms and melodies. <br><br>Gameplay:<br>Layout your note orbs in a classic linear or randomly placed fashion. Use the stone plated as timing indicators, place a pair of trigger totems in any orientation and launch an energy wave to trigger your note orbs from any direction. <br><br>Mechanics<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Tone Wand <br></li><li> 10 Sounds (4 Percussive &amp; 6 Tonal) to experiment with<br></li><li> Tone wand to Set, Retrieve, Trigger the Note orbs<br></li><li> Trigger Totems for triggering Note Orbs from any direction<br></li><li> Routing and trigger poles for connecting, routing and looping the music patterns</li></ul><br>Use sound and resources of the surrounding environment to craft various whimsical instruments.",
  "about_the_game": "Song of a Spirit is a Game Jam submission made in 14 days. It is a crafting game that explores an unconstrained approach to writing tunes, rhythms and melodies. <br><br>Gameplay:<br>Layout your note orbs in a classic linear or randomly placed fashion. Use the stone plated as timing indicators, place a pair of trigger totems in any orientation and launch an energy wave to trigger your note orbs from any direction. <br><br>Mechanics<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Tone Wand <br></li><li> 10 Sounds (4 Percussive &amp; 6 Tonal) to experiment with<br></li><li> Tone wand to Set, Retrieve, Trigger the Note orbs<br></li><li> Trigger Totems for triggering Note Orbs from any direction<br></li><li> Routing and trigger poles for connecting, routing and looping the music patterns</li></ul><br>Use sound and resources of the surrounding environment to craft various whimsical instruments.",
  "short_description": "A music crafting game that decouples you from the 2 dimensional constraints of Time and Pitch, allowing you to play notes in any order from any direction. Explore the world that reacts to music. Write tunes in 3 dimensions. Craft sounds and jam along with your own musical loops.",
